 "can_del": false, "cid": 63205, "create_time": 1648720574, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: 零星的生命不是生命？建议取消封城", "timestamp": 1648720574}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63206, "create_time": 1648720590, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 大部分死的还是本来就有慢性病急性病的老人，没有疫情他们一发病说不定也死了", "timestamp": 1648720590}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63207, "create_time": 1648720649, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 那为什么新冠死亡的老年人在你那里不算零星的生命？", "timestamp": 1648720649}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63210, "create_time": 1648720747, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Alice: “那为什么新冠死亡的老年人在你那里不算零星的生命？”那可以啊，封城会死人，放开也死人，效用函数都是-inf，你觉得对吗？", "timestamp": 1648720747}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63211, "create_time": 1648720816, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 所以放开防疫的国家经济有多好？", "timestamp": 1648720816}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63214, "create_time": 1648720974, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Eve: 说到底你们坚持放开防疫既不是为了健康也不是为了整体的经济，不过是为了个人自私的行为自由而已，为啥不敢说出来呢", "timestamp": 1648720974}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63215, "create_time": 1648721201, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 所以动态清零下的中国经济有多好？GDP数字当然很好看，国家统计局总在说“稳中向好”，失业率也总体稳定。毕竟没有人失业，都灵活就业去了。但实际情况呢，服务业倒闭了多少，找工作有没有变得更难，考研、考公有没有变得更卷，裁员有没有更多，北京开滴滴的司机是不是越来越多了，冷暖自知。", "timestamp": 1648721201}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 63216, "create_time": 1648721261, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text":